Package: tinyconnection
Type: Package
Title: Minimal Yet Compliant Connection Creator
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c(
 person("Dirk", "Eddelbuettel", role = c("aut","cre"), email = "edd@debian.org"),
 person("Mike", "Cheng", role = c("aut","cph")))
Description: Demonstration of the creation of a custom connection without
 upsetting R by not using API accessors. For now the package will only
 work on files. The package is a simplified / modified variant of package
 'rconnection' by Mike Cheng.
URL: https://github.com/eddelbuettel/tinyconnection
BugReports: https://github.com/eddelbuettel/tinyconnection/issues
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
Suggests: tinytest
